Package de.oth.blocklib.threading

Class BlocklibExecutor

java.lang.Object
de.oth.blocklib.threading.BlocklibExecutor
All Implemented Interfaces:
BlocklibExecutorService, java.util.concurrent.Executor, java.util.concurrent.ExecutorService, java.util.concurrent.ScheduledExecutorService
public class BlocklibExecutor
extends java.lang.Object
implements BlocklibExecutorService
The main executor service for the blocklib. All concurrent task should be delegated to this class. Currently supports two different "priorities" TaskPriority.NORMAL and TaskPriority.BACKGROUND. These priorities are handled in such a way that tasks that use them are submitted to different thread pools.
Author:
Loher Florian
